{"tid":2069171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經] 一人一件中學生涯入面最難忘嘅事","createTime":"2020-06-18T07:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:54:17.000Z","uid":154872,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"021fb6c71232b87bf324c5c21758c0f97ed06503","tid":2069171,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"拋舊真人真事磚先，教會學校<br />\n<br />\n每朝都會開早會祈禱，然後神父同老師會出嚟9up下咁<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣就來Halloween，個校監神父出嚟講<br />\n<br />\n叫啲學生唔好去玩嗰啲鬼屋或者扮鬼扮馬<br />\n<br />\n話好危險，會比魔鬼有機可乘<br />\n<br />\n仲講佢以前見過年青人比魔鬼上身，仲正式咁驅過幾次魔<br />\n<br />\n講得唔係好detail，但聽到成間中學啲學生老師一齊呆左喺到<br />\n<br />\n隔咗無耐個神父就上左去搵佢大佬天父爸B了<br />\n<br />\n件事記到而都仲係好震撼"},{"pid":"6a4ce976566ec10395e2e0608d525242a0f09821","tid":2069171,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"食18歲少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfc43a85a9a6756f7da5bba1c5114312057b3ae","tid":2069171,"uid":142106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"蔡高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e46cd5d003019d1fef7dc8aeb698503193454a2","tid":2069171,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:55:52.000Z","msg":"俾同學的入廁所打到郁唔到<br />\n<br />\n仲嘔咗幾啖血<br />\n<br />\n最後自己lan番課室<br />\n<br />\n老師問我做咩遲入班房仲罰我留堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31436d8bf5b35123cb12ca2e21c92e7161a3b9b5","tid":2069171,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"彌撒<br />\n坐地板坐3個鐘<br />\n禮成大叫感謝天主"},{"pid":"40459db48c9c096d0a7757b904f01df778354186","tid":2069171,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dfc43a85a9a6756f7da5bba1c5114312057b3ae","tid":2069171,"uid":142106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"蔡高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad